values: Look at that little trooper! Holding up the roof of the car all by himself! Ganbare yo, Leader!! How such a strong, handsome example of true masculinity was not snapped up sooner, I'll never know. I dunno why Tsuchiya always wants to sit in the passenger seat. All the fun happens in the back >)

I finally did it. I BOUGHT IT. , look look! I BOUGHT IT. You should've seen the clerk's face, it was priceless. I feel like a kid again. The expression was only topped by the one it changed to when I asked where they kept the lotion, and when she said they were out of skincare products I said nevermind, I'd make do without.
